<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/29527881">陆逊，诸葛瑾攻襄阳是哪一年？为什么《吴主传》里是嘉禾三年，《陆逊传》里是嘉禾五年(236年)？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3994103" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content"></div>


</div>
